Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.95,0:00:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.10,0:00:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.27,0:00:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.25,0:00:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.32,0:00:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.39,0:00:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.26,0:00:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.00,0:00:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.24,0:01:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.15,0:01:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.54,0:01:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等妳一個禮拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳一個禮拜後給我答覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.74,0:01:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.05,0:01:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#58 五代還是三鷹?\N女人心今晚決勝負!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.24,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹教練今天好帶勁喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟三鷹教練之間\N出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.41,0:02:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳的樣子跟平常不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.34,0:02:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.65,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了\N我得去車站前的銀行一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不適合愁眉苦臉的表情喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.41,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.18,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩天,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.65,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.96,0:04:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.93,0:04:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.47,0:04:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.11,0:04:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們快來幫我的忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的狗呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,妳是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.76,0:04:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是上次那位…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是妳的狗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,這一隻叫法格拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這一隻叫蒂莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳養了好多小狗喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,因為我很喜歡小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-請問…\N-什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那位男士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說三鷹嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是情侶嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算結婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請妳離開他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.62,0:05:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,怎麼說都太露骨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.06,0:05:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我只不過是\N他相親的對象而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳問三鷹有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.17,0:05:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,他是個很棒的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.47,0:05:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天會很晚回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,今天是禮拜六\N沒有什麼特別的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概傍晚就會回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.25,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.88,0:06:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,那麼請你盡量早點回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人份啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,上街買菜去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.33,0:06:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在高興什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經常碰到妳耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.90,0:07:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,真的好巧喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好巧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.73,0:07:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳找我有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.24,0:07:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個大好機會\N我一定要請她跟三鷹先生分手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.51,0:07:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事\N只是因為小狗往妳這邊走來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.85,0:07:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狗是很坦誠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.62,0:07:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狗喜歡的人絕對不是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.43,0:08:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定是個大好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.94,0:08:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了,波特夫過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.28,0:08:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.02,0:08:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只因為小狗喜歡我\N就把我當作大好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.46,0:08:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來,惣一郎也很喜歡三鷹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.79,0:08:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狗喜歡的人絕對不是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想,他的確是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常溫柔體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.11,0:08:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很關心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.44,0:08:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是對我說,他想跟我在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.66,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.20,0:09:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,想說最近你很少到學校來\N原來是在這裡打工啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來打電話\N想邀你一起去參加班上的聚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.01,0:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而一之瀨大嬸跟我說你在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是今天嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.81,0:09:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,你忘記啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.45,0:09:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是今天我不太方便…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛?有約會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.59,0:09:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是約會啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.33,0:09:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且你的出席率本來就不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.20,0:09:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不趁聚餐的機會多接近教授的話\N會拿不到學分的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.50,0:09:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說我就沒輒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.71,0:09:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代怎麼還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是音無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.63,0:10:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想確認一下明天的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.27,0:10:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,三點,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.94,0:10:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把明天當作是\N決定自己命運的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.45,0:10:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等妳喔,請一定要給我答覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.06,0:10:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳先掛電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼一直說好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.89,0:10:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,哦…沒有,那我掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢自己一個人做決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.78,0:11:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望有人能阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代他一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.69,0:11:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,接下來要去哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.33,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴雖然這麼說\N其實我已經想到一個好地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.47,0:11:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二攤呢?你不參加第二攤嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.97,0:11:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.01,0:11:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼?你在擔心錢的問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.05,0:11:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你盡量早點回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.02,0:11:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那陪我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.19,0:11:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你去你喜歡的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧,反正也談不上是約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他明明說了會早點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛看到我們\N就一副失望的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.01,0:12:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳等的人沒有來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,這一桌真豐盛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然讓管理員痴痴的等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真是罪孽深重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.02,0:12:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個罪孽深重的傢伙\N是三鷹教練?還是五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說喔\N五代很晚才會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是有個叫阪本的朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.47,0:12:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天他打電話來說\N今天他們班上有聚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聚餐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.04,0:12:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就打個電話回來說一聲嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.15,0:12:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,今天是管理員的激勵會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好喝個過癮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼激勵會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.66,0:12:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近妳的心情一直不太好\N所以給妳打打氣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有心情不好,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.03,0:13:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是?只是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要那麼衝嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.87,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟三鷹教練之間\N發生了什麼事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睜眼說瞎話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的表情寫著妳在說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.68,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,這個人最不會說謊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.51,0:13:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係呢\N不要談這種正經八百的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝管理員有個光明的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝房客人人幸福快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.09,0:13:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這瓶葡萄酒真棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個好,這個好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.82,0:13:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去啊,可是沒電車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.26,0:14:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法,叫計程車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?你有計程車錢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.60,0:14:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把全部的財產\N都花在剛才的酒店裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.28,0:14:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那該怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.24,0:14:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.65,0:14:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法?\N什麼辦法?喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他明明說傍晚會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就要回覆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.07,0:15:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.94,0:15:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我說“不要跟他結婚”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有玩通宵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.73,0:15:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了四個小時,我都累慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之平安無事到家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.53,0:16:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安,妳今天起得真早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連大嬸都起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.03,0:16:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是管理員嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.70,0:16:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.75,0:16:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛好紅喔,難道她整晚沒睡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然玩到早上才回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡混了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.72,0:16:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭,大嬸\N這種事不能說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家會害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴\N不要說這種會引起誤會的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.63,0:17:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?\N入浴優待券“奶油哈蜜瓜”?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸,妳好討厭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.27,0:17:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這又是什麼?\N女大學生坐檯的面紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒店的火柴盒上有寡婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.91,0:17:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,這是走在路上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.98,0:17:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到有人在發就收下來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛燒掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.85,0:17:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.76,0:18:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扮得那麼漂亮\N要去哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是跟三鷹約會吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.46,0:18:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是約會的話\N三鷹會開車來接她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人擔心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.10,0:18:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她最近一直愁眉苦臉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員愁眉苦臉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.74,0:18:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一個禮拜真的很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都沒有注意到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.72,0:19:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上\N我們代替五代陪管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.52,0:19:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼問,她都守口如瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.69,0:19:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天管理員好像\N有什麼重要的事要跟你說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.27,0:19:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連晚飯都做好了等你回來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她幫我做晚飯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,還準備了葡萄酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.91,0:19:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,77年份的,真是太好喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.11,0:19:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請你盡量早點回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.78,0:19:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.75,0:19:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩點四十分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.65,0:20:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.22,0:20:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不該為了那種人整晚沒睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.75,0:20:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位,你們要給我勇氣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.62,0:20:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要問三鷹先生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吵醒她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看起來好像很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.92,0:21:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡等她醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.20,0:21:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼音無小姐\N會跟明日菜小姐在一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.07,0:21:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.01,0:21:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這麼重要的時候\N那個愛狗的女孩跑來幹嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.39,0:21:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?大家跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.86,0:21:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉\N我馬上去叫狗的主人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.40,0:22:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.54,0:22:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我喜歡小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.62,0:22:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的,什麼時候睡著的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.66,0:22:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.76,0:22:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.97,0:22:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道三鷹沒有來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.95,0:22:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果那個人一直在睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.25,0:22:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們心情真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.92,0:22:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了什麼開心的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.66,0:22:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像見了那個人似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.90,0:23:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒回過神來啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.57,0:23:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真嚇人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.04,0:23:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我發現了以後\N他居然整個人都痙攣了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.15,0:23:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫救護車比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.86,0:23:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!不要過來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.26,0:23:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走開!走開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.44,0:23:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹跟相親的對象約會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.88,0:23:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求婚的事,到底怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.68,0:23:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.25,0:23:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『心跳不已!\N九條明日菜的初體驗!』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.38,0:23:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟著他一輩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.82,0:24:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我有生以來\N第一次被男人抱在懷裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.11,0:24:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.56,0:24:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.17,0:24:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.41,0:24:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.81,0:25:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.99,0:25:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.19,0:25:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.43,0:25:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.76,0:25:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢…濡濕而發光
